 from sjcostan magnus acs ohio state edu scott j costanzo subject re rfi art of clutchless shifting nntp posting host magnusug magnus acs ohio state edu organization the ohio state university lines seven i used to drive a truck a few years back i once rode with an old codger that had been driving for about three zero yrs the only time he would use the clutch was to get the truck moving he could shift that one three speed lightning quick up or down without the slightest rake of a gear he was as smooth as silk it was the most amazing shifting demonstration i ve ever seen having said all that i still don t know why anyone would want to shift a synchronized tranny without a clutch why do it